# Checker-qualification (negative test) list — <IP_NAME>
# Runs in every regression with +CHKQ_ENABLE and coverage OFF.
# Excluded from IMC merges. A CHKQ_BLIND failure = a checker went blind:
# treat as high-severity; some prior clean report may be unsound.
# Format: <negative_test> <seed> +CHKQ_ENABLE
# [one line per qualified check ID — kept in sync with the check ID
#  inventory in docs/CLAUDE.md]
